{"tid":685822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【沒有最荒謬】廣州男子檢驗愛滋病竟被迫做手術 最後被割包皮","createTime":"2018-05-31T17:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T02:54:05.000Z","uid":14918,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1f4436fc43eda5a9133703d5b29a6bead999bf63","tid":685822,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:15:39.000Z","msg":"廣州男子檢驗愛滋病竟被迫做手術 <br />\n2018/05/30 21:42<br />\n<br />\n內地醫療質素參差，早前曾報道有病人右腳要開刀，醫生竟然開錯左腳，在內地求醫真是要很小心。醫療失誤數不清，不過最荒謬的一宗，可能是一名男子在醫院檢查愛滋病病毒的經歷。 <br />\n<br />\n一次酒後亂性，加上一次的小感冒，廣州的陳先生經歷了男人最痛，他去廣州長安醫院檢查，醫生幫他檢查下體，指他真的有病，要立即做手術，陳先生原本稱要考慮做不做，豈料原來已經「肉隨砧板上」。 <br />\n<br />\n沒有最荒謬，只有更荒謬，手術之後，醫生跟他說原來斷錯症，不要說愛滋病，根本甚麼病都沒有，但醫院臉皮還厚到要收二萬元人民幣費用，雙方目前正在談判。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/011521_1290d5a8141963126b8a4e7a2858921b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F011521_1290d5a8141963126b8a4e7a2858921b.png&h=5ba6f224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/011522_a5c548d49746a5ac2025cb5a2777dc60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F011522_a5c548d49746a5ac2025cb5a2777dc60.png&h=948defd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cca23404ff632a83c0c14335aabd154ce05c6c3","tid":685822,"uid":77235,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57a973226c2c82c0a7d850c76decd77227058a2","tid":685822,"uid":133988,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:06:10.000Z","msg":"佢執到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係割左包皮 唔係割其他仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要還神添啦"},{"pid":"3c879adfa6594eaca126d799b076d804e5e61ed1","tid":685822,"uid":187978,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:16:38.000Z","msg":"厲害了，我的國<br />\n無包皮好過無左個腎"},{"pid":"c17433ae113b0346f6d390137de7462fef8457e0","tid":685822,"uid":66527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:24:44.000Z","msg":"遲d引入內地醫生既話就分分鐘呢d事會發生係我地身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea179bdf23fcd771225e8093bad4cc159f35fc7d","tid":685822,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:25:21.000Z","msg":"內地醫療質素參差，早前曾報道有病人右腳要開刀，醫生竟然開錯左腳，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f752a997327b14c3cb2abf2a46302d0c4f08e7b6","tid":685822,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea179bdf23fcd771225e8093bad4cc159f35fc7d","tid":685822,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:25:21.000Z","msg":"內地醫療質素參差，早前曾報道有病人右腳要開刀，醫生竟然開錯左腳，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:30:09.000Z","msg":"咁濕碎攞黎講，香港閒閒地都左右腦掉轉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8261c31cc2b3e3da8e70de0f32ef22125b97fb8","tid":685822,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea179bdf23fcd771225e8093bad4cc159f35fc7d","tid":685822,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:25:21.000Z","msg":"內地醫療質素參差，早前曾報道有病人右腳要開刀，醫生竟然開錯左腳，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T23:07:30.000Z","msg":"都咪話唔驚<br